  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST OUR UPCOMING GAME</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/5970eba3e32aef05ef994ef508538ae4.webp?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=29 /></span><br><br><strong>Juro Janosik</strong> is an action adventure about a Slovak legendary hero. As Juro Janosik you will take the law into your own hands and take an adventure across country of Slovakia.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You will:</strong></h2><br>Solve many puzzles, handle dangerous obstacles to get to castle:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/9b79bc11d18fe9fea9b69df51fa98384.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/9b79bc11d18fe9fea9b69df51fa98384.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/9b79bc11d18fe9fea9b69df51fa98384.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight with pandurs, tie them up with rope but never kill them because you are \"a good bandit\":<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/0b02ba95a310432e86f13a19661fe633.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/0b02ba95a310432e86f13a19661fe633.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/0b02ba95a310432e86f13a19661fe633.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Search and liberate prisoners:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/42b347c48abdca5c7bd114798be674f5.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/42b347c48abdca5c7bd114798be674f5.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/42b347c48abdca5c7bd114798be674f5.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Steal gold from castles and give it away to poor hardworking villagers:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/45fd50277b3137875dea107968939fb4.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/45fd50277b3137875dea107968939fb4.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/45fd50277b3137875dea107968939fb4.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join my Discord server:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>10 levels with real Slovak castles<br></li><li>many puzzles and dangerous obstacles<br></li><li>upgrading character skills<br></li><li>mechanic for tying up enemies<br></li><li>steam achievements<br></li><li>full gamepad support</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/377010ce2c5301c068517e5a59c65ac5.avif?t=1682967376\" width=194 height=91 /></span><br>* Supported using public funding by Slovak Arts Council",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/5970eba3e32aef05ef994ef508538ae4.webp?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=29 /></span><br><br><strong>Juro Janosik</strong> is an action adventure about a Slovak legendary hero. As Juro Janosik you will take the law into your own hands and take an adventure across country of Slovakia.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>You will:</strong></h2><br>Solve many puzzles, handle dangerous obstacles to get to castle:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/9b79bc11d18fe9fea9b69df51fa98384.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/9b79bc11d18fe9fea9b69df51fa98384.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/9b79bc11d18fe9fea9b69df51fa98384.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight with pandurs, tie them up with rope but never kill them because you are \"a good bandit\":<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/0b02ba95a310432e86f13a19661fe633.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/0b02ba95a310432e86f13a19661fe633.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/0b02ba95a310432e86f13a19661fe633.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Search and liberate prisoners:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/42b347c48abdca5c7bd114798be674f5.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/42b347c48abdca5c7bd114798be674f5.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/42b347c48abdca5c7bd114798be674f5.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Steal gold from castles and give it away to poor hardworking villagers:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/45fd50277b3137875dea107968939fb4.poster.avif?t=1682967376\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/45fd50277b3137875dea107968939fb4.webm?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/45fd50277b3137875dea107968939fb4.mp4?t=1682967376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Join my Discord server:<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>10 levels with real Slovak castles<br></li><li>many puzzles and dangerous obstacles<br></li><li>upgrading character skills<br></li><li>mechanic for tying up enemies<br></li><li>steam achievements<br></li><li>full gamepad support</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/978630/extras/377010ce2c5301c068517e5a59c65ac5.avif?t=1682967376\" width=194 height=91 /></span><br>* Supported using public funding by Slovak Arts Council",
